{"title":"公鸡不鸣，天也会亮（印度谚语）","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"公鸡不鸣，天也会亮（印度谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使在岸边住，也不跟鳄鱼友好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露水不能解渴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公鸡不鸣，天也会亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友情不容草率断绝，再恢复也留下症结。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗在自己的大街上，唯我独尊地称狮子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵志强、王僧道选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}